nde2.errors

Class NDE2Exception

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • nde2.errors.NDE2Exception
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NDE2Exception
extends java.lang.Exception
    A subtype of Exception that is used by the NDE2 API. It is thrown when internal errors happen, or when the server itself returns a problem. If it is a server error, use the ness* properties to determine what it is.
    Author:
    filip
